## Git Ignore File

Create `.gitignore` in root:

```
# Large files
*.pdf
data/pdfs/

# But keep key documents
!resources/kerala_hc_judgment_wpc32516.pdf
!docs/research_paper_final.pdf
!docs/proposed_rbi_master_direction.pdf

# Temporary files
*.tmp
~$*.xlsx
.DS_Store

# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.venv/
```

**Rationale:** 
- Don't upload 100+ case PDFs to GitHub (too large)
- Do upload your key deliverables
- Keep repository clean

